examples.en: The pressures of work can make you ill.

examples.en: The weekend was a welcome break from the pressures of work.

examples.en: The trip was a welcome respite from the pressures of work.

examples.en: I feel I'm not able to cope well with the pressures of life.
examples.ru: Я чувствую, что не в состоянии справиться с жизненным напряжением.

examples.en: He gave in to the social pressures to act and dress like everybody else.

examples.en: Sports provide him with a welcome diversion from the pressures of his job.
examples.ru: Спорт помогает ему отвлечься от давления на работе.
